# Wallet Master — architecture (Variant A)

Full migration plan: `.docs/refactoring.md` (phases, file moves, acceptance criteria, §10 status).

One domain = the same namespace segment across all layers (e.g. `Transactions` everywhere, never `Transaction` in one folder and `Transactions` in another).

## Approved `app/` roots

- `Actions/{Domain}/` — use cases (write + read orchestration), `handle()`, no `Http/Resources`
- `Data/{Domain}/` — DTO, filters, form options, read results (not `ViewModels/`)
- `Http/Controllers|Requests|Resources/{Domain}/` — web layer only
- `Support/{Domain}/` — stateless domain algorithms (no HTTP, no SDK clients)
- `Integrations/{Name}/` — external clients and infrastructure repositories (e.g. Typesense, DescriptionMemory)
- `Imports/` — import workflow and bank adapters (unchanged root)
- `Models/`, `Policies/`, `Jobs/`, `Events/`, `Listeners/`, `Enums/`, `Console/`

Do **not** add `Services/`, `Modules/`, or `ViewModels/` for new code.

## Domain names (always plural in folders)

`Accounts`, `Transactions`, `Transfers`, `Imports`, `Auth`, `Settings`

## Layer responsibilities

| Layer | Does | Does not |
|-------|------|----------|
| **Controller** | `authorize*`, call Action, `Inertia::render` / redirect, toast `message_key`, map via `Resource::collection()->resolve()` | `DB::transaction`, dedupe rules, `selectRaw` aggregations, business date parsing |
| **Form Request** | `rules()`, `authorize()`, build filters (e.g. `getFilters()`) | DB writes |
| **Action** | transactions, `lockForUpdate`, orchestration; returns `Model` / `Collection` / `Data\*Result` | import `Http\Resources\*`, `number_format`, `asset()` |
| **Data** | immutable DTO: `*Filters`, `*Result`, `*FormOptions::toArray()` | `Inertia::render`, Eloquent in DTO classes |
| **Resource** | array shape for Vue/Inertia | authorization, business rules |
| **Support/{Domain}** | pure algorithms (dedupe, relative dates) | HTTP/SDK clients |
| **Integrations** | API clients, infra repositories | wallet business rules |
| **Model** | relations, `casts()`, general scopes (`whereBelongsTo`) | full index workflow (date filters + sort + aggregates) |

## Data flow

- **Write:** `Request` → `Action` → `Model` (+ `Support` / `Integrations`) → redirect + toast.
- **Read (index):** `Request` → `Action` → `Data\*Result` → `Controller` → `Resource` → Inertia.

## Code conventions

- Action: one public `handle()`, prefer `final`.
- Action **never** imports `App\Http\Resources\*`.
- UI presentation (`asset()`, `label_key`, front-facing date format) only in Resource or Enum metadata.
- Integrations: register bindings in `AppServiceProvider`.
- Tests mirror domains: `tests/Feature/{Domain}/`, `tests/Unit/Data/` or `tests/Unit/Support/{Domain}/`.

## Refactoring PRs

One phase per PR (see `.docs/refactoring.md` §7). Update §10 status when done. Run `vendor/bin/pint --dirty` and `php artisan test --compact` (domain filter).

## Where to put a new file

| Need… | Location |
|-------|----------|
| Inertia endpoint | `Http/Controllers/{Domain}/` |
| Request validation | `Http/Requests/{Domain}/` |
| JSON props shape | `Http/Resources/{Domain}/` |
| Business operation | `Actions/{Domain}/` |
| Filters / DTO / form options | `Data/{Domain}/` |
| Domain algorithm | `Support/{Domain}/` |
| External API | `Integrations/{Name}/` |
| DB entity | `Models/` |
| CSV import workflow | `Imports/` |
| Queue job | `Jobs/` + dispatch from Action/Workflow |
| HTTP test | `tests/Feature/{Domain}/` |
| Pure logic test | `tests/Unit/...` |
